com.futurice.cascade.i.action

Interface IBaseAction<IN>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAction<PHANTOM_IN>, IActionOne<IN>, IActionOneR<IN,OUT>, IActionR<PHANTOM_IN,OUT>, IActionTwo<IN1,IN2>, IOnErrorAction<PHANTOM_IN>

    public interface IBaseAction<IN>
    This is a marker interface which other functional interfaces extend Implementing this interface indicates a primary onFireAction, usually one executed asynchronously on an IThreadType
